high_descs: Turn around and stop at the toaster
Grab the knife that's in front of the toaster
Turn around and go straight to the counter
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices
Look up at the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Look down at the counter
Grab a slice of tomato
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn right and go to the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a tomato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter on the right where the toaster is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Go to the left to the microwave, then hang a left and go forward to the counter with the tomato on it.
Use the knife to cut the tomato into slices.
Raise the knife up higher in the air.
Put the knife down on the counter to the left of the tomato.
Look down at the counter.
Pick up a slice of the tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go to the sink, turn to the left to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the tomato when it is done cooking.
Turn around and go forward to the fridge that is on the left.
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toaster.
Pick up the knife in front of the toaster.
Turn around and walk to the tomato on the counter.
Cut up the tomato on the counter.
Look at the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Look at the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a piece of tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Microwave the piece of tomato and then pick up the piece of tomato from the microwave and close the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the piece of tomato on the top left shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of tomato on the top left shelf in the fridge.
